w?"],[4450,4596,"We all know you can't afford anything."],[4679,4792,"Oh, you got me."],[4850,5017,"I guess I didn't learn my lesson in juvie."],[5017,5109,"Joke all you want,"],[5109,5238,"but when I'm done with you,"],[5238,5292,"you're gonna wish"],[5292,5376,"you were behind bars."],[5413,5505,"Can't believe we have to put up"],[5505,5680,"with this poser for the whole season."],[5697,5751,"Yeah?"],[5801,5935,"How much is this rich asshole"],[5935,6068,"paying you to kiss his ass?"],[6189,6293,"You wanna talk about money?"],[6373,6431,"When you're the one"],[6431,6577,"who's begging for service?"],[6577,6656,"Stop! Stop."],[6677,6861,"Pierce, Wyatt's our new employee."],[6923,7023,"What the fuck did you say?"],[7086,7236,"Pierce, he's a good guy, you just-"],[7236,7424,"Why are you taking his side?"],[7436,7507,"He's nothing."],[7520,7657,"He's a waste of space."],[7674,7707,"Yeah."],[7724,7816,"Yeah, save it for my"],[7816,7953,"employee review. - Stop!"],[8058,8162,"Here's your uniform."],[8229,8270,"Thank you."],[9084,9138,"Shit!"],[9175,9342,"If Isabella sees that scar,"],[9380,9484,"she'll realize Wyatt"],[9484,9684,"is actually her long lost brother,"],[9684,9793,"Asher Bradshaw."],[9826,10030,"And if that happens, I'm screwed!"]],"21":[[375,542,"Your ass is fired."],[542,638,"Don't fucking touch me!"],[667,821,"You don't deserve to spit shine"],[821,938,"my fucking shoes. - Quit it!"],[942,1005,"Pierce!"],[1113,1209,"Do you really think Mom and Dad"],[1209,1334,"would hire this convict?"],[1388,1484,"He's an athlete."],[1555,1676,"I thought it was a good fit."],[1710,1805,"A good fit?"],[1860,2110,"He went to juvie for stealing."],[2143,2252,"He has a record."],[2252,2348,"If he keeps running his mouth,"],[2348,2439,"he'll tank the team"],[2439,2619,"before the whole season even starts."],[2623,2769,"Shouldn't people be forgiven"],[2769,2915,"for their past mistakes?"],[2952,3028,"Mistakes?"],[3032,3207,"Is that what we're calling felonies now?"],[3261,34