uld love to find"],[4554,4637,"some common ground,"],[4637,4829,"since he'll be coming home."],[4938,4971,"Wait."],[5242,5301,"Coming home?"],[5388,5555,"Yeah, I figured you'd want to"],[5555,5655,"after all these years."],[5709,5847,"Your room is just how you left it."],[6197,6368,"Wanna come home, Wyatt?"],[6368,6498,"I, I don't..."]],"57":[[37,83,"I don't..."],[525,604,"Screw them!"],[604,767,"The Bradshaw's treated me like shit"],[767,842,"for weeks."],[871,1021,"It's just because I share their blood"],[1021,1180,"that they suddenly give a shit about me."],[1180,1288,"Asher, please."],[1288,1405,"We want you back with us."],[1447,1501,"No."],[1559,1639,"Definitely not."],[1639,1701,"No, but,"],[1701,1793,"we're your family."],[1793,1906,"You're our family."],[2423,2610,"I thought I was just a filthy convict."],[2644,2740,"Not two weeks ago,"],[2740,2907,"you had the cops ready to haul me off."],[2907,3148,"That was a horrible mistake."],[3203,3315,"We were just trying to protect"],[3315,3415,"the Bradshaw name."],[3499,3536,"Listen,"],[3599,3770,"it is difficult being in the public eye."],[3849,3941,"Con artists have tried"],[3941,4099,"to take advantage of us in the past."],[4108,4237,"We really fucked up, Asher."],[4237,4366,"Stop calling me that!"],[4379,4433,"Wyatt,"],[4592,4679,"we've been looking for you"],[4679,4767,"for twelve years."],[4796,5025,"Well, a lot's changed in twelve years."],[5105,5217,"And not just with me."],[5480,5534,"I'm gonna go."],[5739,5814,"It's a shame."],[5985,6106,"I always wanted a brother."],[6352,6514,"But you'd probably be more comfortable"],[6514,6577,"in a cell."]],"58":[[617,688,"Hey, Wyatt!"],[1180,1267,"What are you doing here?"],[1309,1351,"I just,"],[1380,1509,"I wanted another chance"],[1509,1801,"to apologize for everything."],[1885,2010,"I don't want another apology."],[2010,2164,"I just want to go our separate ways."],[2173,2252,"I know, I know,"],[2252,2448,"but I've been racking my brain"],[2473,2623,"on how to make things right."],[2873,2927,"What's this?"],[2977,3148,"Well, I was thinking about"],[3148,3370,"how many moments of your life"],[3370,3445,"that I've missed."],[3478,3611,"You know, going camping,"],[3636,3749,"catching your first fish,"],[3774,3874,"teaching you how to shave,"],[3966,4058,"working out together,"],[4104,4320,"your first crush and the sex talk."],[4404,4512,"So, I thought"],[4512,4713,"I would buy you your first car."],[5376,5492,"Holy shit, Wyatt!"],[5518,5613,"That's a Corvette!"],[5726,5876,"That's worth like $50,000!"],[5930,6043,"More like $100,000."],[6177,6239,"Do you like it, son?"],[7107,7165,"Yeah, there's, uh,"],[7265,7399,"some other firsts you've missed,"],[7453,7507,"Bradshaw."]],"59":[[12,112,"You missed me"],[112,208,"getting my ass kicked,"],[291,362,"day after day,"],[425,613,"by the man that I thought"],[613,684,"was my father."],[838,967,"You missed me dumpster diving"],[1001,1080,"for my next meal,"],[1159,1301,"when he was either too broke"],[1301,1434,"or too drunk to afford it."],[1810,2014,"You missed when I had to go to prison"],[2043,2093,"for him."],[2160,2314,"To rot behind bars in his place."],[2364,2402,"What?"],[2527,2573,"Forget it."],[2761,2865,"You can't buy me back."],[3119,3165,"No,"],[3307,3370,"of course not."],[3382,3420,"Um."],[3474,3712,"I just wanted to make a gesture."],[3745,3799,"I'm sorry."],[4033,4091,"I'll get going."],[5263,5355,"Forget it, dude."],[5367,5505,"I'm not keeping that thing."],[5668,5801,"Doesn't mean you can't test drive it."]],"60":[[12,141,"It's all falling apart."],[158,383,"We'll hire some more muscle to rough"],[383,454,"Asher up. - It's not"],[454,504,"good enough!"],[542,663,"The Bradshaws won't stop"],[663,775,"until he comes home."],[800,942,"If we don't stop them first,"],[942,1088,"it is game over for me."],[1614,1651,"Dad!"],[1664,1705,"Shit."],[1751,1856,"How long has he been there?"],[1897,2072,"Pierce, what are you doing here?"],[2173,2423,"Just seeing if Donny has any advice"],[2423,2540,"on how to get through to Asher,"],[2540,2623,"since he raised him."],[2811,2865,"Raised?"],[2990,3182,"That fucker abused him."],[3261,3420,"Mr. Bradshaw, I would never."],[3420,3449,"I,"],[3524,3699,"I was there for him when he had no one."],[3720,3820,"He had us!"],[4083,4129,"Of course,"],[4129,4200,"if I would have known"],[4200,4275,"he was a Bradshaw,"],[4275,4396,"I would have returned him."],[4421,4562,"I'm your number one fan!"],[5075,5146,"Have you seen my son?"],[5180,5263,"No, Mr. Bradshaw."],[5284,5347,"It's just me."],[5501,5563,"What are you hiding?"],[5872,6043,"I would never lie to you, Mr. Bradshaw."],[6072,6189,"I'm your number one fan."],[6297,6423,"I even have your number inked."],[6769,6831,"It was you."],[6994,7082,"Twelve years ago."],[7219,7323,"You were at the hospital."],[7428,7528,"You took our son!"]],"61":[[20,125,"You took our son!"],[433,658,"Mr. Bradshaw, you have it all wrong."],[692,775,"Why did you take him?"],[892,955,"Answer me!"],[1167,1334,"I was just trying to give him a home!"],[1347,1397,"Home?"],[1422,1564,"You didn't give him a fucking home."],[1601,1693,"You tortured him!"],[1885,2027,"He was a troubled kid!"],[2152,2239,"If you lie to me again,"],[2302,2414,"I'll fucking crush your skull."],[2606,2677,"You're a father!"],[2806,2919,"You have to understand,"],[2998,3148,"I was just trying to be there"],[3148,3236,"for my son!"],[3657,3724,"Your son?"],[3812,3849,"No."],[3903,4037,"I don't know what he's talking about."],[4037,4112,"He's crazy."],[4571,4650,"All this time..."],[4733,4863,"Don't take it out on Pierce."],[4909,5075,"You raised him all these years."],[5555,5847,"If I see you near my family again,"],[5935,6089,"I will fucking kill you."],[6577,6710,"What the fuck!"],[6710,6844,"Sorry, I panicked!"],[6856,6977,"If you don't fix this,"],[7019,7073,"I will make sure"],[7073,7186,"you're locked up in a prison"],[7186,7319,"without a pot to piss in."],[7323,7361,"Got it?"]],"62":[[738,934,"Dad, please, let's talk about this."],[934,1017,"Don't call me that."],[1063,1142,"Your blood kidnapped"],[1142,1213,"my real son."],[1234,1330,"You're just an imposter."],[1514,1564,"Trent."],[1851,2014,"Pierce was a child himself."],[2043,2181,"He's a victim here as well."],[2264,2506,"He's just as much our son as Asher is."],[2673,2919,"I promise, I, I, I had nothing to do with it."],[2965,3053,"I was just trying to help"],[3053,3153,"bring Asher home."],[3274,3382,"If I find out you're lying,"],[3440,3549,"I will kick you out so fast"],[3549,3624,"you won't even have a shirt"],[3624,3670,"on your back."],[3670,3737,"You understand me?"],[4004,4083,"Don't worry about it."],[4083,4183,"Just let him cool down."],[4316,4433,"I couldn't protect Asher."],[4617,4733,"But I will protect you."],[4875,4929,"Thanks, Mom."],[5705,5843,"Wake your ass up, dude."],[5889,5960,"What the hell?"],[5997,6089,"We gotta bounce, man."],[6122,6214,"I got a surprise for you."]],"63":[[45,129,"Where are you taking me?"],[200,358,"I'm not in the mood for games, dude."],[421,454,"No?"],[496,583,"Not even for"],[667,725,"football?"],[1180,1255,"What?"],[1288,1359,"We're the Golden Knights."],[1384,1530,"Yeah, I know who you are."],[1580,1776,"You're, like, all my favorite players."],[1789,1851,"You must be Asher."],[1918,2018,"We hear you got quite the arm"],[2018,2127,"and we were hoping you'd toss"],[2127,2235,"around the pigskin with us."],[2323,2414,"How'd you know that?"],[2786,2831,"Oh."],[3165,3236,"What do you say, kid?"],[3574,3703,"He means well."],[3820,4033,"And it's the LA Golden Knights."],[4304,4383,"Alright, fine."],[4383,4508,"But only if you can keep up."]],"64":[[1376,1484,"Nothing's changed, huh?"],[1555,1705,"As long as that shit lives,"],[1726,1839,"I'm nothing to Trent"],[1860,1993,"but a second-string son."],[2106,2264,"Damn, you ain't kidding."],[2431,2489,"I think he throws"],[2489,2577,"better than you, Coach."],[2631,2786,"Well, he is my son."],[2831,2898,"Tight workout."],[2927,2973,"Keep it up,"],[2994,3040,"you're going to be better"],[3040,3203,"than half those posers in college."],[3203,3261,"Thanks, Brady."],[3290,3319,"Yeah."],[4095,4195,"Oh my gosh."],[4241,4320,"They're serious."],[4446,4525,"You got chops, son."],[4671,4713,"Thank you."],[4863,4975,"You know, I could stand here"],[5005,5163,"and beg you to come home,"],[5230,5301,"but if you won't,"],[5426,5509,"will you at least"],[5563,5668,"come to the game tomorrow night?"],[5780,5880,"I don't know."],[5914,6056,"Every time I'm around you guys,"],[6068,6214,"my life implodes."],[6343,6431,"I'll talk to Pierce."],[6464,6589,"He's part of the problem,"],[6598,6698,"but so is Krista."],[6698,6844,"And honestly, so are you."],[6869,6911,"I just,"],[6990,7169,"I don't know if I'm ready for that."],[7365,7403,"Look,"],[7469,7761,"I can't apologize enough."],[7778,7828,"So stop."],[7962,8158,"And stop showering me with gifts."],[8195,8350,"It's not going to undo what happened."],[8479,8604,"I do appreciate this,"],[8737,8892,"but I'm not a Bradshaw."],[9146,9188,"Thank you."]],"65":[[120,283,"You said you would do anything for me."],[329,421,"You swore it!"],[613,667,"I will."],[667,788,"I, I am, I..."],[896,1001,"I can't do that."],[1101,1192,"I thought we were just going"],[1192,1288,"to cripple him."],[1288,1418,"Not, not this."],[1418,1651,"Trent won't stop until Asher is dead."],[2623,2777,"I have a gun in my bed."],[2994,3094,"But I'm not going to be the one"],[3094,3165,"to pull the trigger."],[3219,3286,"I can't."],[3649,3741,"Think about this."],[4679,4754,"Come on, man."],[5184,5221,"Son."],[5251,5367,"You are pathetic."],[5492,5588,"You're disgusting."],[5680,5814,"You are a disgrace."],[6072,6106,"Son!"]],"66":[[437,521,"Hey, sorry."],[521,625,"Now is just not really"],[625,688,"a good time. - Look,"],[742,863,"ever since you were taken from us,"],[863,942,"Mom and Dad have been"],[1101,1146,"different."],[1146,1192,"Um."],[1230,1322,"Dad"],[1322,1455,"became intensely overprotective"],[1455,1597,"and Mom became obsessed"],[1597,1730,"with the image of a perfect family"],[1730,1810,"to distract herself"],[1810,1889,"from the one she lost."],[1922,1985,"I understand,"],[1985,2127,"but that doesn't make it okay."],[2164,2231,"It doesn't."],[2339,2427,"But for the first time,"],[2427,2581,"I saw this glimmer of hope in them"],[2581,2648,"when they found out"],[2648,2769,"that you're still alive."],[2840,2952,"And I felt it too."],[3390,3632,"Dad said you weren't going to play."],[3978,4116,"I'm hoping you'll change your mind."],[4183,4295,"I'd really like to cheer"],[4295,4412,"for my little brother tomorrow."]],"67":[[37,112,"She has a good look."],[137,225,"Good morning, sweetheart."],[337,462,"Big game tonight, Pierce."],[521,583,"How are you feeling?"],[583,725,"Hey, will you go put on your new gear?"],[763,846,"I want to take a picture."],[892,963,"I'm not going."],[1001,1034,"What?"],[1063,1213,"It's the last home game of the season."],[1276,1322,"I know,"],[1322,1426,"but I also know that"],[1426,1618,"you want Asher out on that field."],[1685,1818,"And he's not going to play if I'm there."],[1856,1960,"I don't want another fight."],[1976,2064,"No, I'm not."],[2139,2373,"Maybe next year we can play as brothers,"],[2373,2427,"but, uh,"],[2481,2631,"tonight should be all about him."],[2761,2848,"That's big of you, son."],[2894,3028,"I am so proud of you."],[3228,3278,"You want to sit down"],[3278,3374,"and grab breakfast with us?"],[3386,3440,"No, no."],[3440,3524,"I got, um,"],[3561,3653,"something to take care of."],[5409,5488,"There he is."]],"68":[[45,162,"Just get away from me."],[221,425,"Asher, you have to listen to me."],[508,642,"You can't go to that game."],[642,738,"You don't have a say"],[771,880,"in what I do anymore."],[905,1009,"You're nothing to me."],[1105,1242,"I know you're upset. - Upset?"],[1418,1647,"You broke me down, day by day."],[1735,1860,"You ruined my record."],[1951,2135,"You sicced your psychotic son on me."],[2168,2323,"I just wanted Pierce to have the life"],[2323,2394,"I couldn't give him."],[2431,2585,"Yeah, well you got what you wanted."],[2652,2806,"He was raised by the Bradshaws."],[2831,3036,"He got everything and I got nothing."],[3140,3274,"And he's still not a better quarterback"],[3274,3324,"than I am."],[3386,3503,"Just stay the fuck away from me."],[3728,3791,"Asher!"]],"69":[[45,191,"Be aggressive!"],[229,308,"B-E."],[308,550,"A-G-G-R-E-S-S-I-V-E."],[550,583,"Alright,"],[629,750,"I know we're missing"],[750,859,"our star quarterback."],[896,971,"But we're going to have to-"],[971,1055,"Oh shit, Coach."],[1055,1142,"Look, it's Wyatt!"],[1405,1484,"It's Wyatt!"],[1747,1835,"Go, Wyatt!"],[2218,2310,"Sorry, I'm late, Coach."],[2406,2452,"No."],[2498,2594,"You're right on time."],[2736,2873,"Alright, what's your play?"],[2907,2948,"Alright."],[3186,3294,"Every time we're on trips"],[3294,3365,"to the field side,"],[3365,3561,"they roll from two to one way too fast."],[3561,3624,"That free safety"],[3624,3753,"is going to get way too far away."],[3753,3853,"We're going to have the same"],[3853,3966,"on the backside, okay?"],[3999,4049,"We're gonna run it as"],[4049,4154,"a skinny post."],[4154,4254,"Alright, we've seen it in the film."],[4254,4316,"We know what we're doing."],[4341,4379,"Got me?"],[4400,4429,"Yep."],[4429,4529,"Alright, on one on one."],[4529,4562,"Ready?"],[4575,4608,"Break!"]],"70":[[2077,2202,"And that's a touchdown"],[2202,2352,"by Wyatt Lewis,"],[2377,2719,"ending the game at 49 to 7!"],[2744,3086,"A massive blow out and historic win"],[3086,3269,"for Riverstone High School!"],[3269,3345,"We won!"],[3345,3578,"That was so incredible!"],[3687,3870,"You made me so proud out there, son."],[3891,4058,"I've never felt like this before."],[4066,4108,"Yeah?"],[4129,4220,"Well, get used to it."],[4270,4300,"Come on,"],[4300,4350,"I've got someone"],[4350,4441,"waiting for you in the locker room."],[5347,5401,"Pierce?"],[5472,5568,"I thought he wasn't coming."],[5705,5797,"Whatever he's doing,"],[5797,5955,"he cannot mess this up for Asher."]],"71":[[25,87,"Jason!"],[166,279,"Good to see you, man."],[283,342,"Trent!"],[354,442,"Great to see you."],[446,538,"Great to see you."],[579,734,"Wow, there he is."],[792,905,"God, what a play!"],[955,1130,"I'm Jason Brown, head scout,"],[1163,1263,"University of Michigan."],[1263,1388,"No way!"],[1409,1484,"My alma mater."],[1514,1597,"Yeah, that's right."],[1643,1718,"You know, I scouted Trent"],[1718,1822,"when he was sixteen."],[1856,2002,"He was my biggest success."],[2081,2152,"And when he told me"],[2152,2327,"he had a boy to rival his legacy,"],[2419,2548,"I just had to come down and see."],[2594,2673,"And was I wrong?"],[2711,2769,"He's got an arm."],[2769,2898,"He's got more than an arm."],[2932,3053,"He's got the whole damn package."],[3157,3244,"Well, thank you, sir."],[3257,3382,"Oh, don't thank me."],[3420,3470,"Thank him."],[3557,3611,"He blessed you"],[3611,3757,"with the genetics of a god."],[3912,4041,"And when I saw you out there?"],[4079,4145,"I knew it."],[4145,4325,"I said, that kid's a Bradshaw."],[4533,4654,"So how about hitting the field up north"],[4654,4742,"after graduation?"],[4829,4888,"Then you carry on"],[4888,4967,"your old man's legacy."],[5088,5234,"Continue on his legacy."],[5301,5422,"That's all this ever is."]],"72":[[221,371,"Yeah, I'm sorry."],[371,471,"I can't do that."],[784,984,"Could you give us a moment?"],[1105,1197,"Yeah, sure, sure."],[1209,1242,"Yeah."],[1368,1463,"Well, if you change your mind,"],[1601,1689,"make sure to give me a call."],[1972,2022,"Thanks."],[2043,2106,"Thanks, Jason."],[2686,2781,"This is a once"],[2781,2907,"in a lifetime opportunity."],[2957,3123,"Michigan is one of the top schools."],[3174,3324,"Yeah, but it's your school."],[3399,3574,"This whole thing is about"],[3574,3749,"carrying on that Bradshaw legacy"],[3749,3883,"you're all so obsessed about."],[3883,4083,"I could give a damn about my legacy."],[4220,4295,"This is for you."],[4295,4425,"You earned this."],[4729,4909,"But I, I get it."],[5038,5138,"Everything you've been through."],[5401,5476,"I'm sorry, son."],[5680,5739,"I really am."],[6022,6085,"I'll leave you alone."],[7453,7590,"Am I making a mistake?"],[8103,8158,"Trent, I-"]],"73":[[75,137,"Pierce,"],[279,358,"what are you doing here?"],[479,604,"Just came to congratulate you"],[604,750,"on the big game, brother."],[867,959,"I'm not your brother."],[1338,1401,"That's right."],[1480,1576,"You're a Bradshaw."],[1705,1860,"Feels good to be on top, doesn't it?"],[1989,2027,"Dude."],[2106,2218,"Just leave me alone."],[2268,2348,"It's not fair."],[2406,2585,"I've busted my ass for twelve years."],[2606,2665,"And just because of"],[2665,2815,"some fucking genetics,"],[2873,3011,"you're handed everything,"],[3053,3194,"and I'm tossed aside?"],[3436,3520,"I tried everything"],[3520,3628,"to get you out of my life."],[3674,3749,"This is on you."],[3991,4033,"Dude."]],"74":[[20,158,"Pierce, you don't have to do this."],[212,342,"We can just go our separate ways."],[387,529,"There are no separate ways."],[583,671,"Like it or not,"],[767,855,"they'll always pit us"],[855,975,"against each other, so,"],[1096,1213,"one of us has to go, brother."],[1609,1893,"They won't stop until you're dead."],[2310,2373,"My son!"],[3958,4041,"Why did you do that?"],[4245,4312,"Because"],[4458,4571,"you're my son."],[4984,5013,"What's-"],[5159,5334,"Mom, Mom, Mom, Mom!"],[5409,5497,"No, stay with us!"],[5497,5593,"Mom, you're gonna be okay!"],[5593,5638,"Krista!"],[5905,5955,"Pierce!"],[6456,6598,"Somebody call 911!"],[7082,7115,"Hello?"],[7115,7294,"I need an ambulance at Riverstone."],[7294,7407,"I'm so sorry."],[7499,7549,"Hey."],[7599,7649,"Mom?"],[7703,7757,"It's okay."],[7903,7970,"No, no, no."],[8066,8087,"No."],[8087,8179,"It was worth it"],[8287,8512,"to hear you call me mom."],[8529,8558,"No."],[8629,8658,"No, no, no."],[8658,8762,"Hey, hey, Mom!"],[8817,8846,"No!"],[9163,9221,"Krista!"],[9246,9321,"I didn't mean to."],[9321,9430,"Where's the fucking ambulance?"]],"75":[[467,521,"Mom."],[729,900,"I hope I look better than I feel."],[1155,1288,"You look like a million bucks."],[1659,1726,"How's Asher?"],[2527,2606,"The doctor said that"],[2606,2719,"you'd make a full recovery."],[3449,3553,"Are those for me?"],[3682,3824,"You took a bullet for me."],[3853,3966,"It's the least I can do."],[4325,4396,"I'm your mother."],[4533,4679,"I'd take a hundred bullets for you."],[4758,4904,"But I like the flowers better."],[5055,5121,"That's good."],[5296,5363,"Where's..."],[5426,5476,"Pierce?"],[5826,5947,"Pierce is facing trial"],[5947,6047,"for attempted murder."],[6085,6243,"He'll be in juvie until he's of age"],[6243,6297,"and then off to"],[6297,6381,"prison with his father."],[6414,6523,"He'll pay for what he's done."],[6698,6902,"And I have the lawyers involved"],[6936,7073,"to scrub your record clean."],[7169,7219,"Really?"],[7219,7278,"Thank you."],[7378,7411,"Well,"],[7486,7678,"I guess everything kind of worked out."],[8174,8308,"Look, I have something"],[8308,8433,"I'd like to say."]],"76":[[41,166,"You all have gone through"],[316,550,"such great lengths to make things right."],[571,763,"I already told them we'd back off."],[784,867,"No, that's not it."],[1126,1234,"You all have worked really hard,"],[1426,1589,"you know, in the past few days."],[1589,1743,"And I really do appreciate that."],[1985,2093,"We can't undo"],[2122,2227,"the past twelve years."],[2227,2318,"Asher, please."],[2318,2369,"Please."],[2369,2423,"Isabella,"],[2460,2519,"let him talk."],[2744,2777,"You know,"],[2957,3107,"my whole life, I felt really alone."],[3165,3365,"Like nobody really had my back."],[3766,3933,"You all made me feel really loved,"],[4195,4437,"protected and cared for."],[4508,4542,"I,"],[4637,4754,"I'd like to be a part of that."],[4929,5071,"If you'll have me, of course."],[5376,5601,"You're our son, Asher Bradshaw."],[5680,5805,"We're here for you, no matter what."],[6644,6756,"Get in here, all of you."],[7090,7319,"I have never been so proud"],[7336,7432,"of our family."],[7686,7899,"Nothing will ever"],[7899,8024,"come between us again."]],"77":[[95,229,"I can honestly say"],[271,429,"that this is the proudest moment"],[429,508,"in my career."],[604,850,"And I am honored to introduce my son,"],[925,1009,"Asher Bradshaw."],[1468,1514,"Thank you."],[1655,1735,"As you know,"],[1818,1985,"I was separated from my family"],[2039,2110,"years ago."],[2239,2394,"It's hard to even think about college"],[2394,2435,"right now,"],[2435,2531,"when it feels like I'm making up"],[2531,2631,"for all that lost time."],[2631,2669,"But,"],[2811,2927,"I'm honored to announce"],[2986,3111,"that I will be continuing"],[3111,3236,"on my father's legacy"],[3236,3378,"at the University of Michigan"],[3415,3499,"as a Wolverine."],[3995,4095,"No, no, no!"],[4095,4212,"That should be me!"],[4279,4421,"That should be me!"],[4496,4592,"That should be me!"],[4617,4783,"That should be me!"],[4821,5013,"My father once stood in this very place"],[5059,5117,"and said,"],[5117,5313,"I know the importance of family,"],[5326,5492,"whether on or off the field."],[5584,5739,"And it makes me feel proud"],[5776,5926,"to know that I finally found mine."]]}